From: SeongJae Park <sj@kernel.org>
Date: Thu, 26 Mar 2026 21:50:21 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] ==== validate goal->nid ====

mm/damon/core: validate damos_quota_goal->nid

node_mem[cg]_{used,free}_bp DAMOS quota goals reduce the node id.  The
node id is used for si_meminfo_node() and NODE_DATA() without proper
validation.  As a result, privileged users can cause out of bounds
memory access using DAMON_SYSFS.  Fix the issues.

Signed-off-by: SeongJae Park <sj@kernel.org>
---
 hkml_cv_bogus/hkml_cv_bogus_zj1__ckl | 0
 1 file changed, 0 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 hkml_cv_bogus/hkml_cv_bogus_zj1__ckl

diff --git a/hkml_cv_bogus/hkml_cv_bogus_zj1__ckl b/hkml_cv_bogus/hkml_cv_bogus_zj1__ckl
new file mode 100644
